<name>SUSPENSION &amp; AXLE</name>
<section id="1002I_S000K" variety="S000K">
<name>SUSPENSION</name>
<ttl id="1002I_S000K_7AX05_T00AN" variety="T00AN">
<name>REAR LOWER ARM</name>
<para id="RM000001G8V00MX" category="A" type-id="80001" name-id="SP0JG-12" from="201202">
<name>REMOVAL</name>
<subpara id="RM000001G8V00MX_01" type-id="11" category="10" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000052Q00000">
<content3 releasenbr="1">
<atten4>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Use the same procedure for the RH and LH sides.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>The procedure listed below is for the LH side.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
</content3>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000001G8V00MX_02" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000001G8V00MX_02_0001">
<ptxt>REMOVE REAR WHEEL</ptxt>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001G8V00MX_02_0002" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000052R00000">
<ptxt>DISCONNECT NO. 3 PARKING BRAKE CABLE ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>(See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000010QV00XX"/>)</ptxt>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001G8V00MX_02_0003" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000052S00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE LOWER CONTROL ARM ASSEMBLY LH</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C229155" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the nut and bolt from the axle housing.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>While fixing the nut in place, loosen and remove the bolt.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C229156" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Remove the nut, bolt and control arm.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>While fixing the nut in place, loosen and remove the bolt.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
